Sentencas: This work studies the electrochemical performance and stability of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 (LSM) and La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 (LSCF) cathodes in a AISI441 interconnect/cathode/YSZ electrolyte half-cell configuration at 800 degrees C for 500 h.
Titulo: Long term behaviors of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 and La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 as cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Ohmic resistance and polarization resistance of the cathodes are analyzed by deconvoluting the electrochemical impedance spectroscopy (EIS) results.
Titulo: Long term behaviors of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 and La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 as cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The LSM cathode has much higher resistance than the LSCF electrode even though the respective cathode resistance either decreases or stays stable over the long term thermal treatment.
Titulo: Long term behaviors of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 and La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 as cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: During the 500 h thermal treatment, dramatic elemental distribution changes influence the electrochemical behaviors of the cathodes.
Titulo: Long term behaviors of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 and La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 as cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Chromium diffusion from the interconnect into the LSM electrode at triple phase boundaries (TPBs) leads to segregation of Sr away from La and Mn.
Titulo: Long term behaviors of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 and La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 as cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: For the LSCF cathode, Sr and Co segregation is dominant.
Titulo: Long term behaviors of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 and La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 as cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The fundamental processes at the TPBs are proposed.
Titulo: Long term behaviors of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 and La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 as cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Overall, LSCF is a much preferred cathode material because of its much smaller resistance for the 500 h thermal treatment time.
Titulo: Long term behaviors of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 and La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 as cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells
